From 731ca594efef5dc616375fdd9e87284adec5354b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: David Bauer <mail@david-bauer.net>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 19:47:13 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: mt76: mt7915: receive noisefloor statistics from
 firmware

Some MT7915 boards report idle power values instead of idle power
indicator values. These are not retrieved from the current codepath
reading the undocumented registers.

Instead activate noisefloor notifications from device firmware.
Calculate noisefllor from IPI or IP values depending on which one are
available.

Signed-off-by: David Bauer <mail@david-bauer.net>
